 Healthy Living With Tosin: Maintaining A Plant Based Lifestyle In Lagos On this episode of ‘Healthy Living With Tosin’, blogger and writer, Tosin Ajibade shares tips to maintaining a plant based diet in Lagos. Tosin talks the challenges, costs, where to shop and also the kinds of herbs and spices that can be grown in the garden. Dedicated to living a vegan lifestyle, Tosin is a blogger documenting bits of her bitter-sweet vegan journey since 2019. Watch the video below: 